  assertOperational: vi.fn(),
  setKillSwitch: vi.fn(),
}));

// ── db/client pulls in the better-sqlite3 native binding which cannot load in this
//    sandbox shell (Node-ABI mismatch). The audited units here set `c.auth` directly and
